mil.nga.giat.geowave.store.index

Class BasicIndexModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.store.index.BasicIndexModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Persistable, DataReader<CommonIndexValue>, DataWriter<Object,CommonIndexValue>, CommonIndexModel

    public class BasicIndexModel
extends Object
implements CommonIndexModel
    This class is a concrete implementation of a common index model. Data adapters will map their adapter specific fields to these fields that are common for a given index. This way distributable filters will not need to handle any adapter-specific transformation, but can use the common index fields.
